title: High
overview: Miguel, a young teen from the province, was invited by his sister Gabby to go to Manila, only to find out that she already went to Paris as a prize from a game called High. In Manila he meets Mariel, his sister's neighbor, and discovers that Gabby never left for Paris and was kidnapped by a dark-web syndicate which is behind the underground game. Can Miguel find and save Gabby from danger?
